<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.10.8">
<l>māṇāki vaiya maḷantatuvum vāḷavuṇaṉ</l>
<l>pūṇākaṅ kīṇṭatuvu mīṇṭu niṉaintiruntēṉ</l>
<l>pēṇāta valviṉai yēṉiṭa rettaṉaiyum</l>
<l>kāṇēṉnāṉ kaṇṇa purattuṟai yammāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I was soon thinking of [his] measuring the world as a brahmin</l>
<l>And [his] splitting the jeweled chest of the sword demon;</l>
<l>[So] I of harsh fate who did not worship [you before]</l>
<l>Do not perceive any suffering, lord who dwells in Kaṇṇapuram.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
